data.title: E Le Jeune : 47 Strada Cavallerizza, Naples
data.meta_description: Carte-de-visite full length photograph of Alfonso, Prince of the Asturias, made in a studio. In the background there is a trompe loeil scene featuring a stone house, a flight of stone steps and foliage. The subject is shown from a frontal view and turns his head towards the right of the image. He rests his left arm on a studio prop resembling a rocky outcrop. He crosses his left leg over his right. The subject is wearing national military uniform decorated with a double row of gilt buttons...
